	   <tr><td colspan=2>I agree with Vit on this one. This belt would benefit an enchanter more than any class. I'm not saying that it would be a stupid thing to give it to another class, but... For an enchanter both INT and CHA are very very important. Maxxing out your CHA as an enchanter is top priority, mez not sticking sucks. Concentrating this much INT and CHA in the Belt of all things frees up the other slots for resists. So no, this is not an enchanter only belt. But enchanters will get more use out of it than any class, hands down. And with the lack of good chanter gear out there this should go to the enchanter. All the other classes that would like this can go find better. Enchanters have very few belts better than this. <br>&nbsp;<br>Futen<br>Mad Chanter of Torv</td></tr>
